description: There's nothing like picking up something magnificent from Picanha House! This is Houston's premier source of homemade Brazilian food that's always made to order. Come try the authentic menu, featuring the very best of the best in South American style. Whether you're hungry for the Picanha, Feijoada, Bife Acebollado, or anything else from their stupendous menu, these folks will never let you down. This is food made with love, and we're sure you and your family will be able to taste that in every single bite!
name: Picanha House
